{"tid":1109585,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(丁可欣)你唔好以為許志安單嘢可以令你件事 暫時淡忘啊 完咗件事繼續狙擊你","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T10:38:09.000Z","uid":191047,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3212099f1bb0f81dff6cdbd73726cd2e96f0147e","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mfu1sRe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfu1sRe.jpg&h=8137ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃心穎胸壓攬住啜 <br />\n 許志安背Sammi偷食馬明女友<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/523286211342366/permalink/837420079928976/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F523286211342366%2Fpermalink%2F837420079928976%2F&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM%2BisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=2c5a961c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/523286211342366/permalink/837420079928976/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0577Rp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0577Rp.png&h=788d1c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前《蘋果》得到一條車廂偷情的短片，男主角是有婦之夫許志安，女主角是跟馬國明熱戀中的黃心穎，兩人竟然背另一半搞「安心偷食」真人騷！整條短片長約16分鐘，片段開首見到安仔、心穎和男友人坐在車廂後座，男友人堅持先送心穎返家，戴了黑色口罩的心穎竟爆粗反對：「唔好扮嘢啦！X你！兜X咗我先？」<br />\n<br />\n由大坑到鯉魚門短短10多分鐘車程，「安心」連環激咀逾20次，全程由心穎採取「主攻」情挑安仔，不停攬他狂打茄輪，其中一次纏綿遊戲錫了近1分鐘，咀到啜啜聲，熱情如火的心穎邊咀邊將手放在安仔腿部附近游走；當車輛駛入隧道後，心穎再次飛擒大咬狂咀安仔，咀完後忘形到連口罩都戴歪了，其間隱約聽到心穎說：「...返屋企，唔好驚喎！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5X6DYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5X6DYD.jpg&h=db1579d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算在「休戰」空檔，心穎都「電兔」上身胸壓安仔，捉安仔隻手又捽又玩手指，甚至當安仔是攬枕，將左腳騎在他的身上，啜面錫耳，還用手指幫安仔抹走嘴上的唇膏，風騷入骨。安仔忘記了自己的人夫身份，雖然9成時間都是心穎「主攻」，但安仔卻表現受落，還主動錫了心穎面珠一啖，更越坐越低，似乎擔心被隔鄰車輛發現，而心穎相當識做，咀完就戴口罩遮樣，又不停幫安仔拉下cap帽遮掩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qhnciK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qhnciK.jpg&h=a5475bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而被網民封為心穎BB的她，原來私底下竟是「世界級姣精」，終於可以在後座跟安仔獨處時原形畢露，馬上隔住口罩咀了安仔一啖，10秒後意猶未盡的她，索性除口罩埋身攬安仔啜嘴，表現猴擒。咀完後，兩人繼續十指緊扣，之後隱約聽到心穎說：「so sad...我好悶...教徒」跟住拉開安仔隻手不再緊拖，安仔惟有順勢將手貼在心穎大腿上，3秒後忍唔住又撩心穎十指緊扣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwVczxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwVczxd.jpg&h=e5763666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然，當晚心穎表現看似有點醉意，更不時「鬼妹仔」上身大講英文，但差不多抵達目的地時，本來嗲聲嗲氣跟安仔說話的她，竟忽然轉tone跟司機說：「去到燈位轉右，唔該！」似乎酒醉至少都有8分醒。而安仔除了有點疲態，亦不覺有醉酒。兩人到心穎香閨後齊齊落車，後事如何？只有他們兩人最清楚！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOYmsSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOYmsSj.jpg&h=6b068062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而「安心偷食」極大可能發生於本月3日，事關當日心穎曾在IG上載跟安仔、方力申、劉浩龍、梁漢文、丁子高等出席男友人生日飯局的照片，當晚二人的打扮，跟在車廂的衣服一模一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBfoGcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBfoGcr.jpg&h=f47315fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eoQW1cz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeoQW1cz.jpg&h=5d575d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Giid3q3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiid3q3.jpg&h=c204304f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n51歲許志安（安仔）和鄭秀文（Sammi）經歷分手、復合到結婚，走過考驗才許下婚姻的盟誓，3年前黃子華為Sammi演唱會擔任嘉賓，就以「香港最後一個童話」來形容他們的愛情故事。<br />\n<br />\n今年是兩人結婚5周年紀念，不過，這個愛情「童話」，從今天起，或要幻滅了！安仔將於今晚7時假銅鑼灣一間酒店舉行記者會交代「安心事件」。"},{"pid":"f11427aff5a15d4863196acabe70b4ee32f7527a","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QiBgM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QiBgM7.jpg&h=b11c5724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18av5Fv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18av5Fv.jpg&h=d2103c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0x6D0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0x6D0y.jpg&h=504e7154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnFTi0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnFTi0z.jpg&h=9c93691b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxdp97f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcxdp97f.jpg&h=58b11992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph6OSkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph6OSkB.jpg&h=b22897c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJP1sTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJP1sTX.jpg&h=599ff852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KH9T3si.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKH9T3si.jpg&h=7818e58a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b42ccbe4e7c41956624d164fb70e7fcaaafd919","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhEkJsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhEkJsp.jpg&h=8c99bf75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYzAxkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYzAxkM.jpg&h=54e3abf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eCRP7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eCRP7s.jpg&h=3ecd8f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Ds6D0O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Ds6D0O.jpg&h=c4858f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07kPBNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07kPBNu.jpg&h=cdb39ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcPdi0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcPdi0Q.jpg&h=7c08b749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6O2ckR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6O2ckR.jpg&h=0eeedaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJX2WNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJX2WNx.jpg&h=de2f9664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0d4743d42524c03b653e6ff2aeedd40cae61b65","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HD3UNUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHD3UNUz.jpg&h=b5128dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事件主角許志安宣佈將於今晚7時假銅鑼灣一間酒店舉行記者會交代事件，約下午5時44分，現場已有過百傳媒在現場排隊等入場。<br />\n<br />\n日前《蘋果》得到一條車廂偷情的短片，開始時為許志安、黃心穎與一名男友人坐在車廂後座，原本男友人提議先與安仔一起送心穎返家，但心穎爆粗反對，其實安仔撐心穎，更向男友人訛稱自己先返家，再等心穎自己回家。但男友人下車後，心穎原形畢露，兩人在車廂內激咀，咀到啜啜聲，熱情如火的心穎邊咀邊將手放在安仔腿部附近游走，甚至咀到口罩都歪了。看似被動的安仔表現受落，還主動錫了心穎面珠一啖，其後更一同返心穎香閨。"},{"pid":"5834c6977c5b1f72d1a6c0ad986d82d012ee3d3c","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢件事有個共通點<br />\n黃心穎同丁可欣都係雞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2t0v5Hz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2t0v5Hz.jpg&h=b1f5e95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfEg1gn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfEg1gn.jpg&h=96b04ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQq0Jve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQq0Jve.jpg&h=1203c9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkF77WV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkF77WV.jpg&h=87b16150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kC2WQW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kC2WQW.jpg&h=5807bf8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9NqUCC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9NqUCC.jpg&h=3d4e635d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXytSpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXytSpk.jpg&h=2e922251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRWLaa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRWLaa1.jpg&h=d645c65e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9bfd2ef48ca35dce868e5850aee258d7d9a08ad","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【安心偷食】<br />\n黃心穎形象插水 傳無綫抽起劇集唔播</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DVaggRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDVaggRY.jpg&h=4b2a1956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">30歲黃心穎背住男友<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">馬國明</span>跟已婚的許志安偷食</span>，轟動全城。心穎入行7年是非和緋聞一樣多，被封「<span style=\"color: pink;\">姣Wing</span>」，但今次跟已婚安仔偷食斷正，形象直插谷底，<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉無綫已決定將她工作叫停</span>，包括心穎主演的劇集《<span style=\"color: gold;\">堅離地愛堅離地</span>》，原本定於下月13日晚緊接《鐵探》推出，<span style=\"color: red;\">但有傳無綫決定抽起。</span>"},{"pid":"aa81e34ee1d466b27333d0b4908cb47d03cd7fcd","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃心穎靠關係黐許志安 <br />\n鄭秀文早聞「狐狸」曾踩場突擊！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayoNoyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayoNoyz.jpg&h=e689ca50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據知情人士透露，Sammi早就感應到有「狐狸」的出沒，並有意無意都走到安仔身邊，所以她就曾試過突擊上Gym Room，展示正印氣勢，之不過「狐狸」又怎會害怕，不但與Sammi「交心」做好友，齊齊做運動，Sammi還大讚對方是「標準穎」。"},{"pid":"36532988c57c16d44d47943659aca5568ee423f4","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【疑似陳煒聲帶流出】傳黃心穎拍劇黐人夫 王浩信：我諗嗰位同事誤會咗</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQMGs1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQMGs1c.jpg&h=8d466691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許志安和黃心穎車廂偷食事件，哄動全城。網上即有不少移花接木圖片，用馬國明拍《降魔的》劇照載住黃心穎和許志安。而WhatsApp亦有一條45秒錄音，稱是陳煒力數黃心穎，陳煒今日否認是她錄音，說：「大家聽過我把聲都知我把聲唔係咁樣，講嘢語氣唔係咁樣啦，咁條聲既然唔係我，我都唔雖要回應。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑似陳煒錄音中，更一度點名批評王浩信，王浩信當年與黃心穎在上海、無錫拍劇集《東坡家事》外景，經常出雙入對，有指王浩信拍劇期間陪玩陪食，將老婆陳自瑤和囡囡拋諸腦後。對於疑似陳煒聲帶，王浩信今日回覆傳媒時話：「我諗嗰位同事誤會咗，我喺《東坡家事》裏邊同心穎係飾演一對夫妻，佢見我蹺住佢或拖住佢，應拍攝當中或排戲，戲外絕對冇呢啲情況發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">網傳聲帶內容如下：<br />\n嗰時我同萬綺雯返大陸做嘢，嗰時都係同歐陽震華、王浩信嗰套，吖唔記得叫咩名，吖《東坡家事》，佢同王浩信拖手啦，肯定同王浩信有景轟啦。跟住有次去宣傳，佢同萬綺雯講啱啱先去蘭桂芳飲完酒，嘩，真係嗰時都知佢係嗰啲wet 妹玩玩下。佢同馬明都唔方耐，肯定貪馬明儍下儍下咁啦。</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"7aa9027eafa7a527ad2cabd79ccd48d67ef64dbf","tid":1109585,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kHctQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kHctQ.jpg&h=24e97195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APthLOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPthLOU.jpg&h=d5b28e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ot6ZY8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot6ZY8V.jpg&h=d71eba58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WxnctW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WxnctW.jpg&h=cc5fa344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGr7oAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGr7oAC.jpg&h=3603b259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjwGs2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjwGs2j.jpg&h=784eb54e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}